UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc2='I don\'t care to hear it, $N. Nope, no way are you going to be let into the Searing Gorge. Impossible. Not going to happen. How many times do I have to tell you - I can\'t let you in! Do you not speak common? Are you an orc in disguise? N-O. NO!$B$BIf I let you in, then I have to let everybody in. Pretty soon your close friends will want in, then their distant relatives, then their friends, and so on and so forth. The last time that happened... well, we won\'t talk about the last time it happened.',Text0_1_loc2='I don\'t care to hear it, $N. Nope, no way are you going to be let into the Searing Gorge. Impossible. Not going to happen. How many times do I have to tell you - I can\'t let you in! Do you not speak common? Are you an orc in disguise? N-O. NO!$B$BIf I let you in, then I have to let everybody in. Pretty soon your close friends will want in, then their distant relatives, then their friends, and so on and so forth. The last time that happened... well, we won\'t talk about the last time it happened.',Text1_0_loc2='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc2='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=1833;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc2='What can you do at an inn?$B$BWell when you stay at an inn, you rest very comfortably.  Because of this, you will become "well rested" much more quickly than you would in the wilderness.  When you are well rested, you learn more from experience.$B$BYou may also speak with any innkeeper to get a hearthstone, and can later use the hearthstone in order to quickly return to that inn.',Text0_1_loc2='What can you do at an inn?$B$BWell when you stay at an inn, you rest very comfortably.  Because of this, you will become "well rested" much more quickly than you would in the wilderness.  When you are well rested, you learn more from experience.$B$BYou may also speak with any innkeeper to get a hearthstone, and can later use the hearthstone in order to quickly return to that inn.',Text1_0_loc2='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc2='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=1853;
