Text0_0_loc2='I was the last to die. As I felt my spirit leaving my mortal shell, I swore a blood oath.$B$B<Prince Toreth shakes his head.>$B$BA pact was made between this land and I: My blood for this world. I became the sole keeper of the history of my people.$B$BI cannot rest until I am secure in knowing that the story of the dragon riders of Loreth\'Aran is not lost in the passages of time.'
