Text0_0_loc2='Thank goodness for you!  Claw and I were investigating this place when we were jumped by Swamplord Musel\'ek.  He can control animals, even druids!$B$BUnfortunately, Claw was caught in bear form at the time, and is now the swamplord\'s pet.  I don\'t dare change into cat form or he\'ll get me too!$B$BI\'m afraid you\'ll have to fight Claw in order to save him.  Just keep heading west; you can\'t miss him.'
