Text0_0_loc2='How embarrassing to be taken as a pet by a hunter!$B$BI owe you my life, but please, trouble yourself no longer with my welfare.  Now that you\'ve freed me from Musel\'ek, I\'ll be able to find my way out.  Maybe I\'ll pick up Rayge along the way.'
