Text0_0_loc2='Good work! Arthas now knows about the plagued grain in Stratholme, and is about to begin the culling. Something is still not quite right, though. I sense a foreign presence in this timeline besides us, and that must mean the Infinite Dragonflight are here somewhere.',Text0_1_loc2='Good work! Arthas now knows about the plagued grain in Stratholme, and is about to begin the culling. Something is still not quite right, though. I sense a foreign presence in this timeline besides us, and that must mean the Infinite Dragonflight are here somewhere.'
Text0_0_loc2='I don\'t know, and that worries me. I\'ll do everything I can to find the Infinites. What I need you to do now is stay close to Arthas by joining his army.',Text0_1_loc2='I don\'t know, and that worries me. I\'ll do everything I can to find the Infinites. What I need you to do now is stay close to Arthas by joining his army.'
Text0_0_loc2='Well, you\'re not going to sign recruitment papers or anything, but you are going to fight alongside him. You need to make sure Arthas culls Stratholme and defeats Mal\'Ganis. Without Uther and Jaina around, he\'ll need all the help he can get. If you talk to Arthas, he\'ll put you to work destroying the forces of Mal\'Ganis. Follow along until I can figure out what\'s going on with the Infinites. I\'ll contact you again when I know more.',Text0_1_loc2='Well, you\'re not going to sign recruitment papers or anything, but you are going to fight alongside him. You need to make sure Arthas culls Stratholme and defeats Mal\'Ganis. Without Uther and Jaina around, he\'ll need all the help he can get. If you talk to Arthas, he\'ll put you to work destroying the forces of Mal\'Ganis. Follow along until I can figure out what\'s going on with the Infinites. I\'ll contact you again when I know more.'
